  <p style="color: var(--foreground); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">The Douglas Baby Fox Teether Plush ($87.86) is a premium investment for safety-conscious parents. Yes, $88 is steep for a baby toy. But here's the honest part: you're getting Douglas brand quality, a 100% silicone teether ring (baby-safe, no BPA), baby-safe embroidery with zero small detachable parts, and a genuinely adorable plush companion. Perfect for teething relief and cuddles. If you compare it against buying a $25 generic teether AND a $35 cute plush separately ($60 total), the Douglas fox is the integrated, quality-first choice. Great for parents who prioritize safety over cutting costs.</p>
