      <p style="margin: 0;">Yes. The 100% silicone teether ring is baby-safe, non-toxic, and BPA-free. All embroidery is baby-safe stitching—zero loose threads or small detachable parts. Recommended for 3+ months (when teething typically begins). Newborns (0-3 months) can have the plush as a comfort toy with supervision, but the teether ring is primarily for teething-age babies.</p>
