    <div style="margin-top: 1rem; padding-top: 1rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--foreground); line-height: 1.6;">
      <p style="margin: 0;">Sophie ($25, Vibe Score 72) is rubber-only with a minimalist design—iconic and legendary. Douglas Fox ($87.86, Vibe Score 77) offers teether PLUS plush, more baby appeal, and Douglas heritage. Sophie is the cultural icon; Douglas is the premium combo. Different choices: Sophie if you want "the" classic teether, Douglas if you want integrated safety and design. Sophie is cheaper and iconic; Douglas is more multifunctional.</p>
